      • SCHEMA_EVOLUTION_COLUMNS

        public static final String SCHEMA_EVOLUTION_COLUMNS
        The desired TABLE column names and types for input format schema evolution. This is different than COLUMNS and COLUMNS_TYPES, which are based on individual partition metadata. Virtual columns and partition columns are not included
